(476, 54, 1, 1, 'Subject-matter mastery is directly and fully addressed by PLO1, which focuses on demonstrating a comprehensive understanding of the key theories and concepts in sport coaching. A weight of 1.0 is assigned because this is the sole and primary PLO that targets disciplinary knowledge.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(477, 54, 1, 2, 'Critical-thinking is primarily developed through PLO5 (0.6), which requires students to systematically analyze various factors and resources to arrive at well-informed decisions. PLO2 (0.4) contributes by requiring students to develop and evaluate instructional plans, which inherently demands critical appraisal of alternatives.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(478, 54, 1, 3, 'Problem-solving skills are equally distributed between PLO2 (0.5), which involves designing effective instructional plans to address learning challenges, and PLO4 (0.5), which requires creating solutions for the complex problem of catering to individual student differences.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(479, 54, 1, 4, 'Research and adaptive thinking are primarily driven by PLO6 (0.6), which explicitly requires active engagement in scholarship and contributing to the knowledge base. PLO3 (0.4) contributes by requiring the use of current and emerging technologies, which demands novel and adaptive thinking.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(480, 54, 2, 8, 'The desire for life-long learning is the core and explicit focus of PLO6, which is about actively engaging in scholarship by learning from and contributing to the knowledge base in education. A weight of 1.0 is assigned as this PLO is the sole direct match.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(481, 54, 4, 13, 'Embracing diversity is the central theme of PLO4, which is about creating successful learning environments by catering to individual differences among students. This directly requires embracing and valuing diversity in all its forms.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(482, 54, 4, 14, 'Professional and ethical conduct is directly and fully addressed by PLO7, which is to apply professional ethics in all educational contexts. A weight of 1.0 is assigned as this is the sole and explicit PLO targeting ethical conduct.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(483, 54, 5, 19, 'Management skills are integral to PLO2, which involves developing and managing comprehensive instructional plans to optimize student learning outcomes. Effective plan management requires organizational and managerial competencies.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(484, 54, 5, 21, 'Leadership is the explicit focus of PLO8, which is to lead positive change in education. This PLO directly requires students to develop and exercise leadership skills to drive educational improvement.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:09', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(485, 53, 1, 1, 'Subject-matter mastery is fully and directly addressed by PLO1, which focuses on demonstrating knowledge and competencies in sport management across various settings. A weight of 1.0 is assigned as this is the sole PLO explicitly targeting disciplinary knowledge mastery.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:31', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(486, 53, 1, 2, 'Critical-thinking skills are explicitly named in PLO3 (0.5) and are equally developed through PLO5 (0.5), which requires collecting and analyzing data to understand sport management situations. Both PLOs demand rigorous analytical reasoning.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:31', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(487, 53, 1, 3, 'Problem-solving is equally addressed by PLO2 (0.5), which requires applying knowledge to real-world settings and solving practical challenges, and PLO5 (0.5), which involves analyzing industry issues and developing data-driven solutions.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:31', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(488, 53, 1, 4, 'Research and novel thinking are best represented by PLO5, which explicitly involves collecting appropriate data and analyzing complex situations related to sport management and industry issues. A weight of 1.0 reflects this direct alignment.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:31', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(489, 53, 3, 10, 'Effective communication skills are the explicit and sole focus of PLO4, which requires students to communicate orally and in writing within various sports settings and to different stakeholders. A weight of 1.0 reflects this direct and complete alignment.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:31', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(490, 53, 3, 11, 'Awareness of local, regional, and international issues is an explicit component of PLO3, which requires applying skills with specific reference to local, regional, and international contexts. A weight of 1.0 is assigned for this direct alignment.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:31', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(491, 53, 4, 14, 'Professional and ethical conduct is an explicit component of PLO3, which mentions awareness of ethical/legal and social responsibility issues as a core learning outcome. A weight of 1.0 reflects this direct alignment.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:31', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(492, 53, 5, 19, 'Management skills are a core component of PLO1, which is about demonstrating knowledge and competencies specifically in sport management. The program\'s primary disciplinary focus is management, making this a direct and complete alignment.', '', '2026-02-20 13:39:31', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(513, 7, 1, 1, 'Subject-matter mastery is developed by applying critical thinking and demonstrating problem-solving skills in the major fields of chemistry.', '', '2026-02-21 14:17:22', '2026-03-01 10:17:28'),
(514, 7, 1, 2, 'Critical-thinking is a direct outcome of applying critical thinking in the major fields of chemistry.', '', '2026-02-21 14:17:22', '2026-03-01 10:17:28'),
(515, 7, 1, 3, 'Problem-solving is the core of this PLO, which focuses on demonstrating problem-solving skills in the major fields of chemistry.', '', '2026-02-21 14:17:22', '2026-03-01 10:17:28'),
