(1073, 41, 5, 19, 'This competency is developed by demonstrating knowledge of effective management of public health programs.', '', '2026-02-22 17:40:18', '2026-03-01 09:47:35'),
(1074, 41, 5, 20, 'Not explicitly evidenced in the stated PLOs; potential coverage may exist at course/activity level, but it is not demonstrable from the program-level PLO statements.', '', '2026-02-22 17:40:18', '2026-03-01 09:47:35'),
(1075, 41, 5, 21, 'This competency is developed by applying leadership skills in public health.', '', '2026-02-22 17:40:18', '2026-03-01 09:47:35'),
(1076, 45, 4, 16, 'This competency is developed by promoting the oral and systemic health of the public at large.', '', '2026-02-22 18:10:22', '2026-03-01 09:24:29'),
(1081, 54, 2, 5, 'Self-awareness is equally fostered by PLO6 (0.5), which requires engaging in scholarship and self-reflection on one\'s own knowledge gaps, and PLO7 (0.5), which involves applying professional ethics and thus requires self-assessment of one\'s own conduct and values.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1082, 54, 2, 6, 'Adaptability is primarily developed through PLO4 (0.6), which requires flexible and adaptive teaching methods to cater to individual differences. PLO3 (0.4) supports this by requiring students to utilize emerging technologies, which demands continuous adaptation to new tools.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1083, 54, 2, 7, 'Adaptive thinking is equally cultivated through PLO4 (0.5), which requires adapting instructional approaches to diverse student needs, and PLO5 (0.5), which requires systematically analyzing various factors to make well-informed decisions in dynamic educational settings.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1085, 54, 3, 9, 'Being cultured, in the context of education, involves understanding and respecting diverse backgrounds and perspectives. This is fully encapsulated in PLO4, which focuses on creating successful learning environments by catering to individual differences among students, requiring cultural sensitivity.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1086, 54, 3, 10, 'Effective communication is essential for developing and delivering instructional plans (PLO2, 0.5), as it requires clear communication of learning objectives and feedback. It is equally important for leading positive change in education (PLO8, 0.5), which requires persuasive communication with colleagues, administrators, and the community.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1087, 54, 3, 11, 'Awareness of local and international issues is developed through PLO4, as creating successful learning environments that cater to individual differences requires an understanding of the diverse local and international backgrounds, cultures, and contexts that students bring to the classroom.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1088, 54, 4, 12, 'This competency is not explicitly addressed by the program\'s PLOs. While Islamic ethics may be embedded in the broader professional ethics of PLO7, there is no direct and explicit reference to Arabic-Islamic identity in the stated learning outcomes.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1091, 54, 4, 15, 'Being civically engaged is a key component of leading positive change in education, which is the focus of PLO8. Civic engagement in education means actively working to improve educational outcomes for the broader community.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1092, 54, 4, 16, 'Community and global engagement is an outcome of leading positive change in education (PLO8), which extends beyond the individual classroom into the broader community and global educational landscape.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1093, 54, 5, 17, 'Creativity and innovation are equally required in developing novel and effective instructional plans (PLO2, 0.5) and in leading positive change in education (PLO8, 0.5), which requires innovative thinking to challenge the status quo and propose new educational approaches.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1094, 54, 5, 18, 'Collaborative skills are essential for creating successful learning environments that cater to individual differences (PLO4), which often involves collaboration with students, parents, and other educators to design and implement inclusive learning experiences.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1096, 54, 5, 20, 'Interpersonal skills are fundamental to PLO4, which requires interacting effectively and empathetically with a diverse student body to understand their individual needs and create successful learning environments.', '', '2026-03-01 07:49:01', '2026-03-01 07:49:01'),
(1102, 53, 2, 5, 'Self-awareness is developed through PLO2 (0.5) by applying skills in real-world settings, which provides experiential feedback for self-reflection and growth, and PLO3 (0.5) by understanding one\'s own ethical and social responsibilities in a professional context.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1103, 53, 2, 6, 'Adaptability is primarily developed through PLO2, which requires students to effectively apply their knowledge and skills in various real-world settings, each presenting unique challenges that demand flexible and adaptive responses.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1104, 53, 2, 7, 'Adaptive thinking is the core of PLO3, which involves applying critical thinking and reasoning skills across local, regional, and international contexts. This requires students to continuously adapt their thinking frameworks to different cultural and regulatory environments.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1105, 53, 2, 8, 'The desire for life-long learning is fostered by PLO2, which encourages field experiences and volunteerism. These real-world exposures create a habit of continuous learning by confronting students with novel challenges that require ongoing knowledge acquisition.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1106, 53, 3, 9, 'Being cultured is developed through PLO1 (0.5) by understanding the broader relationship between the sport industry and society, and PLO3 (0.5) by applying skills in local, regional, and international contexts, which requires cultural awareness and sensitivity.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1109, 53, 4, 12, 'This competency is not explicitly addressed by the program\'s PLOs. While ethical conduct is addressed in PLO3, there is no direct and explicit reference to Arabic-Islamic identity in the stated learning outcomes.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1110, 53, 4, 13, 'Embracing diversity is addressed by PLO1 (0.5) through understanding the relationship between the sport industry and a diverse society, and PLO3 (0.5) by applying skills in diverse international contexts, which requires recognizing and valuing different perspectives.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1112, 53, 4, 15, 'Being civically engaged is directly encouraged by PLO2, which explicitly promotes field experiences and volunteerism as means of applying knowledge in real-world settings, both of which are core expressions of civic engagement.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1113, 53, 4, 16, 'Community and Global Engagement is fostered by PLO1 (0.5) through understanding the industry\'s broader relationship with society, and PLO2 (0.5) through volunteerism and field experiences that directly connect students with their community.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1114, 53, 5, 17, 'Creativity and innovation are required in PLO5 to analyze complex situations and propose novel, data-driven solutions for sport management and industry issues. Analytical problem-solving inherently requires creative thinking to generate new approaches.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1115, 53, 5, 18, 'Collaborative skills are essential for effective communication with different stakeholders, as outlined in PLO4. Communicating effectively with diverse stakeholders requires a collaborative mindset and the ability to work across different groups.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1117, 53, 5, 20, 'Interpersonal skills are fundamental to effective communication with various stakeholders in sport, as described in PLO4. Strong interpersonal skills are a prerequisite for the oral and written communication demanded by this PLO.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1118, 53, 5, 21, 'Leadership skills are developed through PLO2, where students apply knowledge and skills in real-world settings, often taking on leadership roles in field experiences and volunteer activities, which are explicitly encouraged by this PLO.', '', '2026-03-01 07:50:15', '2026-03-01 07:50:15'),
(1707, 42, 1, 1, 'This competency is developed through demonstrating excellence in clinical practice.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
(1708, 42, 1, 2, 'This competency requires being critical consumers of research, which hones critical-thinking skills.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
(1709, 42, 1, 3, 'This competency is developed by being patient-centered practitioners committed to shared decision-making, which involves problem-solving.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
(1710, 42, 1, 4, 'This competency is developed by being critical consumers of research and evidence-informed practitioners.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
(1711, 42, 2, 5, 'Not explicitly evidenced in the stated PLOs; potential coverage may exist at course/activity level, but it is not demonstrable from the program-level PLO statements.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
(1712, 42, 2, 6, 'Not explicitly evidenced in the stated PLOs; potential coverage may exist at course/activity level, but it is not demonstrable from the program-level PLO statements.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
(1713, 42, 2, 7, 'Not explicitly evidenced in the stated PLOs; potential coverage may exist at course/activity level, but it is not demonstrable from the program-level PLO statements.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
(1714, 42, 2, 8, 'This competency is developed by demonstrating commitment to the development of the profession, which requires life-long learning.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
(1715, 42, 3, 9, 'This competency is developed by demonstrating emotional and cultural intelligence.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
