(1718, 42, 4, 12, 'Not explicitly evidenced in the stated PLOs; potential coverage may exist at course/activity level, but it is not demonstrable from the program-level PLO statements.', '', '2026-03-01 09:54:59', '2026-03-01 09:54:59'),
